  "title": "*Urgent*  15 Months Data Engineer - (up to $6500) - West  #NJE",
  "description": "<ul><li>Support Deployment Principal to communicate, onboard, and support suppliers in execution of Product Traceability Compliance programs using Deployment principal approved messaging</li><li>Develop and optimize APIs and SQL queries for efficient data extraction on a biweekly basis </li><li>Create and maintain interactive dashboards using  Excel and Tableau / Power BI</li><li>Implement and manage data ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) processes </li><li>Collaborate with platform vendors to ensure data accuracy and accessibility </li><li>Develop reports to present insights and recommendations to stakeholders</li><li>Monitor <a href=\"mailto:traceability@nike.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">function</a> email inbox, escalate to appropriate teams and respond directly per guidance</li><li>Develop and maintain communication calendar and deployment timeline</li><li>Meeting scheduling, notes, and recaps</li><li>Document and maintain program FAQs and responses</li><li>Develop, deploy, and analyze supplier survey on program feedback </li><li>Perform validations in product traceability platform as needed per guidance (e.g., supplier requests to delete incoming transactions)</li></ul><p>Joy Yeow Zhi Qian<br />(CEI Registration No: R2096261)<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA Licence No: 99C4599)</p>",
